<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.2">
<l>muttum maṇiyum vayiramum naṉpoṉṉum</l>
<l>tattip patittut talaippeytāṟ pōleṅkum</l>
<l>pattu viralum maṇivaṇṇaṉ pātaṅka</l>
<l>ḷottiṭ ṭiruntavā kāṇīrē yoṇṇuta līrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with bright-foreheads, come and see the way the feet</l>
<l>of the gem-hued [Lord] and all [his] ten toes beat harmoniously and settle,</l>
<l>every part [of him] is as if [it were] a gift of pearls, gems, and diamonds</l>
<l>collected and set in good gold. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
